review_data: Reviewed in the United States on August 19, 2021
name: P. OKeefe
title: Nuts are way too small
review: This would have been awesome if the nuts were big enough to chew or small enough to not need to chew. As it was, they were an awkward size that meant I was swallowing them without chewing them even though they were too big to be swallowed. Tried a couple of bites, pushed the yogurt around to see if it was just a bad couple of spoonfuls, but every nut was that same size. Into the trash it went.
